# LinkedList Practice in Java

This folder contains Java programs based on LinkedList collection framework concepts.

## Topics Covered

- Creating LinkedList
- Adding Elements
- Removing Elements
- Searching Elements
- Iterating LinkedList
- Reversing LinkedList
- Sorting LinkedList
- Queue using LinkedList
- Stack using LinkedList
- Removing Duplicates
- Comparing LinkedLists

## Technologies Used

- Java
- Collection Framework
- LinkedList Class

## Purpose

These programs are written for:
- Strengthening Java Collection concepts
- Improving problem-solving skills
- Preparing for coding interviews
- Practicing GitHub project organization